&lt;p&gt;Maybe cancel out the double-negative in:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;blockquote&gt;&lt;p&gt;It will, however, not mean that a new version of the Lucene can&apos;t read an old version within the same major version.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;

&lt;p&gt;to something like this (rough draft)?&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This change only affects the Fieldable API; other backwards&lt;br/&gt;
